net.sf.mmm.util.lang.api.attribute

Interface AttributeWriteMinimumValue<VALUE>

  • Type Parameters:
    VALUE - is the generic type of the minimum value. This is typically a Number but may potentially also be something else (e.g. a Date). Should be the same type as AttributeReadValue.getValue().
    All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeReadMinimumValue<VALUE>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    UiWidgetAdapterDoubleField, UiWidgetAdapterIntegerField, UiWidgetAdapterIntegerSliderField, UiWidgetAdapterLongField, UiWidgetAdapterNumberField<VALUE>, UiWidgetAdapterRangeField<VALUE>, UiWidgetDoubleField, UiWidgetIntegerField, UiWidgetIntegerSliderField, UiWidgetLongField, UiWidgetRangeField<VALUE>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractUiWidgetDoubleField, AbstractUiWidgetIntegerField, AbstractUiWidgetIntegerSliderField, AbstractUiWidgetLongField, AbstractUiWidgetNumberField, AbstractUiWidgetRangeField, DoubleSpinBox, IntegerRangeBox, IntegerSpinBox, LongSpinBox, NumberBox, NumberSpinBox, UiWidgetAdapterGwtDoubleField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtIntegerField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtIntegerSliderField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtLongField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtNumberField, UiWidgetAdapterTestDoubleField, UiWidgetAdapterTestIntegerField, UiWidgetAdapterTestLongField, UiWidgetAdapterTestNumberField, UiWidgetDoubleFieldGwt, UiWidgetDoubleFieldTestImpl, UiWidgetIntegerFieldGwt, UiWidgetIntegerFieldTestImpl, UiWidgetIntegerSliderFieldGwt, UiWidgetIntegerSliderFieldTestImpl, UiWidgetLongFieldGwt, UiWidgetLongFieldTestImpl

    public interface AttributeWriteMinimumValue<VALUE>
extends AttributeReadMinimumValue<VALUE>
    This interface gives read and write access to the minimum value of an object.
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)

    • Method Detail

      • setMinimumValue

        void setMinimumValue(VALUE minimum)
        This method sets the minimum value of this object.
        ATTENTION:
        Changing the minimum value dynamically can invalidate the current value. This should be avoided as it may have undesired effects.
        Parameters:
        minimum - is the new maximum value to set. Use e.g. Integer.MAX_VALUE to unset.
